Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:05.04,English,,0,0,0,,Good morning class. Welcome to our first class.\N{\rChinese}早上好，大家！欢迎来到我们的第一节课。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.10,English,,0,0,0,,And today,\N{\rChinese}今天，我想做的是提供……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.56,English,,0,0,0,,what I want to do is provide the\N{\rChinese}what I want to do is provide the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.46,English,,0,0,0,,framework for how we will learn this semester.\N{\rChinese}本学期学习的框架。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.16,English,,0,0,0,,What are we learning? How are we learning?\N{\rChinese}我们在学什么？我们怎么学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.90,English,,0,0,0,,Why are we learning? Alright, so\N{\rChinese}我们为什么学？好了，开始吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.70,English,,0,0,0,,this is a class of ideas.\N{\rChinese}这是一堂关于思想的课。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.28,English,,0,0,0,,So it's really important for you to pay attention\N{\rChinese}所以你们认真听讲非常重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:31.16,English,,0,0,0,,and understand how these ideas connect with each other.\N{\rChinese}并且要理解这些思想彼此之间的联系。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:36.18,English,,0,0,0,,If I'm not being clear, ask me a question.\N{\rChinese}如果我说得不清楚，问我一个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:41.10,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, make it a habit to ask as many questions as possible\N{\rChinese}实际上，养成尽可能多问问题的习惯。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,because that way you will learn more,\N{\rChinese}因为这样你会学得更多。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:48.08,English,,0,0,0,,learning will be more fun for you, and learning will be much more clearer to you, okay?\N{\rChinese}学习会更有趣，学习也会更清晰，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.28,English,,0,0,0,,So let's get in the habit of asking questions.\N{\rChinese}让我们养成提问的习惯吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.70,English,,0,0,0,,So wherever I am confusing,\N{\rChinese}只要我说得不清楚，随时打断。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:57.28,English,,0,0,0,,wherever I'm speaking too fast, wherever you don't understand,\N{\rChinese}无论我说得多快，还是你不懂，随时打断。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.38,English,,0,0,0,,interrupt me, okay?\N{\rChinese}让我们养成提问的习惯。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.26,English,,0,0,0,,Let's get in the habit. Alright, so\N{\rChinese}好了，开始吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:05.44,English,,0,0,0,,I first want to\N{\rChinese}我先想说说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:10.50,English,,0,0,0,,talk about Immanuel Kant.\N{\rChinese}伊曼努尔·康德。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.52,English,,0,0,0,,We will be discussing him a lot this semester because\N{\rChinese}本学期我们会多谈他。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,he is the greatest philosopher in Western history.\N{\rChinese}他是西方史上最伟大的哲学家。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.30,English,,0,0,0,,And he teaches us,\N{\rChinese}他教给我们，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:25.50,English,,0,0,0,,he taught us how the world works.\N{\rChinese}他教我们世界是怎样运作的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.16,English,,0,0,0,,And this is what he told us.\N{\rChinese}这就是他告诉我们的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:28.66,English,,0,0,0,,He told us that\N{\rChinese}他告诉我们，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:33.94,English,,0,0,0,,we can\N{\rChinese}我们可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:37.18,English,,0,0,0,,never know the objective reality.\N{\rChinese}从未曾知晓客观实相。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.46,English,,0,0,0,,There is an objective reality,\N{\rChinese}有客观实相，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.40,English,,0,0,0,,what he calls the nomina,\N{\rChinese}他所称之名词。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:44.96,English,,0,0,0,,okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.88,English,,0,0,0,,Or the things in...\N{\rChinese}或者是那里的事物……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:54.38,English,,0,0,0,,themselves. That\N{\rChinese}本身。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.70,English,,0,0,0,,is not knowable to us.\N{\rChinese}它不为我们所知。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.44,English,,0,0,0,,That is a world we can never access.\N{\rChinese}那是我们永远无法触及的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.72,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Because\N{\rChinese}为什么？因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:05.34,English,,0,0,0,,we perceive the world through our senses.\N{\rChinese}我们通过感官感知世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:11.90,English,,0,0,0,,Our senses, our perception warps the world\N{\rChinese}我们的感官与感知扭曲世界，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.84,English,,0,0,0,,and changes it into a structure\N{\rChinese}并将其变为结构。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:18.36,English,,0,0,0,,that we can process called the phenomena.\N{\rChinese}我们可以处理的那部分叫做现象。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.54,English,,0,0,0,,And we build\N{\rChinese}然后我们构建……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:36.30,English,,0,0,0,,Ub Ub\N{\rChinese}Ub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.66,English,,0,0,0,,Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub\N{\rChinese}Ub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.84,English,,0,0,0,,Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub\N{\rChinese}Ub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:45.42,English,,0,0,0,,Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub Ub understand reality we need to add in time\N{\rChinese}Ub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:49.92,English,,0,0,0,,and space and that's the example all right\N{\rChinese}和空间，这就是例子，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,so how the world works is we perceive the world we perceive the nomina and\N{\rChinese}所以世界运作的方式是我们感知世界，我们感知名词并且……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:03.52,English,,0,0,0,,turn it into the phenomena for us to process in other words and\N{\rChinese}把它转化为现象，以便我们处理，换句话说……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:09.16,English,,0,0,0,,this is really important reality is what we imagine it\N{\rChinese}这件事真的很重要，现实就是我们想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.94,English,,0,0,0,,to be there is no objective\N{\rChinese}在那里没有客观的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:17.84,English,,0,0,0,,reality reality is what we imagine it to be\N{\rChinese}现实就是我们想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:23.50,English,,0,0,0,,life is a constant process a constant act of imagination\N{\rChinese}生命是一场不断的过程，一场不断的想象行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:29.22,English,,0,0,0,,all right that's that's Emmanuel Kant that's the\N{\rChinese}好的，就是这样，埃马纽埃尔·康德的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.46,English,,0,0,0,,first idea i want you to understand\N{\rChinese}第一点，我想让你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.18,English,,0,0,0,,so\N{\rChinese}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:38.66,English,,0,0,0,,what i want i want to do in this class this semester is train you or\N{\rChinese}我想在这学期的这门课里做的事是训练你，或者说教你，或者激发你去扩展你的想象力。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:44.82,English,,0,0,0,,teach you or inspire you to augment your imagination\N{\rChinese}teach you or inspire you to augment your imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.26,English,,0,0,0,,so that\N{\rChinese}于是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.02,English,,0,0,0,,you see the world much more clearly\N{\rChinese}你会更清晰地看到世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:54.76,English,,0,0,0,,this class is not about what to think it's about how to think\N{\rChinese}这门课不是讲什么想法，而是讲怎么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:04.54,English,,0,0,0,,all right all right so\N{\rChinese}好的，好的，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:08.68,English,,0,0,0,,let me explain the structure of the course\N{\rChinese}让我来解释一下这门课的结构。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:13.28,English,,0,0,0,,so there's past there's present\N{\rChinese}先是过去，再是现在。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:16.08,English,,0,0,0,,and there's future\N{\rChinese}还有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:25.16,English,,0,0,0,,we'll be looking at all three this semester the past the present\N{\rChinese}我们将在本学期把过去、现在和未来都放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.76,English,,0,0,0,,and the future we were analyzing all three\N{\rChinese}我们正在分析这三者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.64,English,,0,0,0,,in order to construct a more\N{\rChinese}为构建更客观的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:34.88,English,,0,0,0,,objective reality for ourselves we will\N{\rChinese}我们将会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:38.10,English,,0,0,0,,not succeed we will fail but\N{\rChinese}我们会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.14,English,,0,0,0,,the process is going to be a real process we will not succeed we will fail but\N{\rChinese}过程将是真正的过程，我们会成功，我们会失败，但…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:44.62,English,,0,0,0,,the process of trying will train our minds to think much more critically about the world\N{\rChinese}尝试的过程将训练我们的思维，使我们更批判性地思考世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:48.40,English,,0,0,0,,so let me explain how in the\N{\rChinese}所以让我来解释如何在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:54.28,English,,0,0,0,,present we have geopolitics we'll be studying geopolitics\N{\rChinese}现在我们有地缘政治，我们将学习地缘政治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.64,English,,0,0,0,,for example why is there war in Ukraine why\N{\rChinese}例如，为什么乌克兰会有战争，为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:03.42,English,,0,0,0,,is there war in the middle east what will happen we'll be studying geopolitics\N{\rChinese}为什么中东会有战争，接下来会怎样，我们将学习地缘政治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:07.48,English,,0,0,0,,and we'll try to understand why this is happening\N{\rChinese}我们会尝试理解这件事发生的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:12.98,English,,0,0,0,,we'll try to formulate an analytical model of geopolitics.\N{\rChinese}我们会尝试构建一个地缘政治的分析模型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? An analytical model.\N{\rChinese}好的？一个分析模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.70,English,,0,0,0,,We will then\N{\rChinese}我们随后会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,use this analytical model to make predictions about the future.\N{\rChinese}用这个分析模型来预测未来。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.50,English,,0,0,0,,Why do we do this? Because\N{\rChinese}我们这么做的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.94,English,,0,0,0,,these predictions will tell us if\N{\rChinese}这些预测会告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.14,English,,0,0,0,,our analytical model is correct or not.\N{\rChinese}我们的分析模型是否正确。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}好的？这样说通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.72,English,,0,0,0,,It's no different from artificial intelligence.\N{\rChinese}它与人工智能没有区别。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:43.90,English,,0,0,0,,How do you know if your artificial intelligence, the model is correct or not?\N{\rChinese}你怎么知道你的人工智能模型是否正确？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.36,English,,0,0,0,,When you test it against reality.\N{\rChinese}当你把它与现实对照时。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? There's no difference between that\N{\rChinese}好的？那两者之间没有区别。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.50,English,,0,0,0,,artificial intelligence system and what we're trying to do here.\N{\rChinese}人工智能系统和我们在这里尝试的东西没有区别。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.46,English,,0,0,0,,And why are we doing this?\N{\rChinese}我们为什么要这么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,Because if we're able to have an actual model\N{\rChinese}因为如果我们能有一个真正能做出正确预测的模型，那就可以把这一切都拿回去分析过去。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.98,English,,0,0,0,,that makes correct predictions, then\N{\rChinese}我们可以把这一切都拿回去分析过去。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.56,English,,0,0,0,,we can take all this and go back and analyze the past.\N{\rChinese}我们可以把这一切都拿回去分析过去。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.22,English,,0,0,0,,To reveal the secret\N{\rChinese}揭示世界的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.22,English,,0,0,0,,history of the world.\N{\rChinese}历史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:18.66,English,,0,0,0,,That is a project we are undertaking this semester.\N{\rChinese}这是一项我们本学期正在进行的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:24.96,English,,0,0,0,,To discover for ourselves the secret history of humanity.\N{\rChinese}为我们自己发现人类的秘密历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.66,English,,0,0,0,,Because you may not know this,\N{\rChinese}因为你可能不知道这一点，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.34,English,,0,0,0,,but all the history that you learn in school, all\N{\rChinese}但你在学校学到的所有历史，全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:35.68,English,,0,0,0,,that history that you think you know, it is\N{\rChinese}你以为自己知道的那段历史，实际上是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.48,English,,0,0,0,,false. Okay?\N{\rChinese}是假的。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.44,English,,0,0,0,,The history that you know, the history\N{\rChinese}你所知的那段历史，那个历史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.38,English,,0,0,0,,that you believe,\N{\rChinese}你所相信的那段历史，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:46.44,English,,0,0,0,,is a system implanted into\N{\rChinese}是由强大的人们植入你们大脑中的系统。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.02,English,,0,0,0,,your brains by powerful people.\N{\rChinese}your brains by powerful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:54.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So the real question that we're looking at this semester is really,\N{\rChinese}好的？所以本学期我们真正要探讨的核心问题是，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.08,English,,0,0,0,,how does\N{\rChinese}那么，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.74,English,,0,0,0,,power work?\N{\rChinese}权力是如何运作的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:04.08,English,,0,0,0,,work. Because\N{\rChinese}工作。因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:08.50,English,,0,0,0,,if we can figure this out, then you will achieve liberation,\N{\rChinese}如果我们能搞清楚这点，随后你就能获得解放，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:13.82,English,,0,0,0,,you achieve freedom, you understand how you're being manipulated by others.\N{\rChinese}你获得自由，你就会明白别人是怎样操控你的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.44,English,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you'll be free,\N{\rChinese}于是你就自由了，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,you'll be empowered to live the way you want to live,\N{\rChinese}你将有能力按自己的方式生活，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:26.78,English,,0,0,0,,to see the world that is true to you. So\N{\rChinese}去见证真正属于你的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:32.36,English,,0,0,0,,let me give you three career examples of how power works.\N{\rChinese}让我给你举三个职业例子来说明权力是怎么运作的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, the first example is money.\N{\rChinese}好的，第一个例子是钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.60,English,,0,0,0,,Let us do a thought experiment.\N{\rChinese}让我们做一个思考实验。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:52.16,English,,0,0,0,,I'm a bank, okay, I decide I want to open a bank.\N{\rChinese}我是一家银行，好的，我决定开一家银行。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.66,English,,0,0,0,,And now you're allowed to put money in the bank.\N{\rChinese}现在你们可以把钱存进银行。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so all of you get together and\N{\rChinese}好了，大家一起把钱放进去。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,you put $5 million in the bank.\N{\rChinese}你把500万存进银行。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.98,English,,0,0,0,,Not $5 million. Now, why do you put $5 million into my bank?\N{\rChinese}不是500万。现在，为什么你把500万存进我的银行？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.94,English,,0,0,0,,Because I promise you 1% interest.\N{\rChinese}因为我答应你1%的利息。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.08,English,,0,0,0,,Right? 1% interest.\N{\rChinese}对吧？1%利息。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.98,English,,0,0,0,,That's a really good deal. But now because\N{\rChinese}这真是个好交易。可现在因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.16,English,,0,0,0,,I owe you some money, right, I owe you 1% interest,\N{\rChinese}我欠你钱，对吧，我欠你1%利息。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.46,English,,0,0,0,,I now need to go make money for myself.\N{\rChinese}我现在需要去为自己赚钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.98,English,,0,0,0,,So I have a friend who's building a restaurant\N{\rChinese}于是我有个朋友正在建一家餐厅。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,and he says, I need $5 million to build a restaurant.\N{\rChinese}他说：我需要500万来建餐厅。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:48.70,English,,0,0,0,,And after a year, I will pay back 10% interest.\N{\rChinese}一年后，我会付10%的利息。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:57.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? 10% interest. And so\N{\rChinese}好的？10%的利息。于是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.08,English,,0,0,0,,I make a 9% profit and I can use that to pay my employees,\N{\rChinese}我赚了9%的利润，可以用来支付员工。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.54,English,,0,0,0,,to pay myself a salary, to build a new building.\N{\rChinese}给自己发工资，建一座新楼。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:08.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So now I want you to think about this.\N{\rChinese}好？现在请你们想想这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.52,English,,0,0,0,,I'm a bank, I got $5 million in deposit money,\N{\rChinese}我是银行，我存了500万。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.00,English,,0,0,0,,then I gave out a $5 million loan.\N{\rChinese}然后我发了5百万的贷款。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.68,English,,0,0,0,,Today, how much money do I have?\N{\rChinese}今天，我手里有多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.44,English,,0,0,0,,How much money is in the bank? Countless.\N{\rChinese}银行里有多少钱？无数。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.78,English,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Countless.\N{\rChinese}嗯？无数。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.88,English,,0,0,0,,How much money now do I have?\N{\rChinese}现在我手里有多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:31.36,English,,0,0,0,,I got $5 million from you guys, then I gave it out to someone else.\N{\rChinese}我从你们那里拿了500万，然后又发给别人。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So how much money is in the bank right now?\N{\rChinese}对吧？现在银行里有多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.44,English,,0,0,0,,Zero. Zero, right?\N{\rChinese}零。零，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.12,English,,0,0,0,,It should be zero.\N{\rChinese}应该是零。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.22,English,,0,0,0,,Logically, the answer is zero.\N{\rChinese}逻辑上答案是零。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:50.26,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, zero is the answer that you are taught in economics.\N{\rChinese}实际上零就是你们在经济学里学到的答案。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.96,English,,0,0,0,,It's what you are taught.\N{\rChinese}这就是你们学到的答案。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:56.30,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Zero is not an answer that we're taught in economics.\N{\rChinese}是吗？零不是我们在经济学里学到的答案。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:59.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. You cannot loan all the money that you have.\N{\rChinese}好的。你不能把所有的钱都贷出去。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.40,English,,0,0,0,,Like, for example, they will have a limit,\N{\rChinese}比如说，他们会有一个额度限制。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.18,English,,0,0,0,,like 25%,\N{\rChinese}像25%，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.48,English,,0,0,0,,I don't know, maybe 10%, so you can only loan like $4 million.\N{\rChinese}我不知道，可能10%，所以你只能贷大约400万美元。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.34,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, yeah. Okay. Really good point.\N{\rChinese}好的，好的，嗯。真的很好的点。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.18,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Oh, yes. Okay. So that's really good.\N{\rChinese}好的。哦，是的。好的。所以这真的很好。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.80,English,,0,0,0,,So in economics, you learn about the idea of the five -year balance.\N{\rChinese}在经济学里，你会学到五年平衡的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. And you learn about the idea of the fractional reserve system.\N{\rChinese}好的。你还会学到分数准备金制度的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.24,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? What's fractional reserve?\N{\rChinese}好的？什么是分数准备金？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:29.12,English,,0,0,0,,As you say, you must leave behind a certain amount of money.\N{\rChinese}正如你所说，你必须留存一定金额的现金。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.94,English,,0,0,0,,It could be 7%, it could be 10%, it depends on the country.\N{\rChinese}可以是7%，也可以是10%，取决于各国。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:36.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Let's say 10%. So theoretically, I cannot actually lend out $5 million.\N{\rChinese}好的？设定10%。理论上，我就不能真正借出500万。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.78,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lend out $4.5 million.\N{\rChinese}我准备借出450万。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? You're right.\N{\rChinese}好的？你说得对。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:45.12,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's law as well.\N{\rChinese}好的？这也是法律。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好的？那么，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:52.46,English,,0,0,0,,actually, okay,\N{\rChinese}实际上，好的，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.82,English,,0,0,0,,let's say I lend out $4.5 million.\N{\rChinese}设定我借出450万。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now how much money do I have in the bank?\N{\rChinese}好的？现在我在银行里有多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.82,English,,0,0,0,,$2.5 million.\N{\rChinese}250万。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.24,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, half a million. Right?\N{\rChinese}是的，五十万。对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So again, this is what you're taught in economics.\N{\rChinese}好的。那么，再说一次，这就是你在经济学里学到的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.72,English,,0,0,0,,This is what makes logical sense.\N{\rChinese}这就是逻辑上成立的结果。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.26,English,,0,0,0,,Right? The correct answer,\N{\rChinese}对吗？正确答案是，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.10,English,,0,0,0,,what actually happens in real life,\N{\rChinese}实际生活中发生的事是，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:15.80,English,,0,0,0,,is you now have $9.5 million.\N{\rChinese}你现在手里有950万。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. That is the correct answer.\N{\rChinese}好的。那是正确答案。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.36,English,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense.\N{\rChinese}这没有道理。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.76,English,,0,0,0,,Right? But it happens in reality.\N{\rChinese}对吗？但它在现实中发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.04,English,,0,0,0,,And how do we know? Because over the past 20 years,\N{\rChinese}而我们怎么知道呢？因为过去20年里，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.56,English,,0,0,0,,Chinese banks, like the Bank of China,\N{\rChinese}中国银行，如中国银行，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.08,English,,0,0,0,,the Bank of Industry and Commerce, the Agriculture Bank of China,\N{\rChinese}中国工商银行、农业银行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.46,English,,0,0,0,,if you Google these banks,\N{\rChinese}如果你在谷歌搜索这些银行，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.92,English,,0,0,0,,what you will see is these past 20 years,\N{\rChinese}你会看到过去20年的情况，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.52,English,,0,0,0,,these banks have become the largest in the world.\N{\rChinese}这些银行已成为世界上最大的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:51.00,English,,0,0,0,,How did that happen? Was it\N{\rChinese}那是怎么回事？是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.98,English,,0,0,0,,because Chinese people got rich and put all the money in the bank?\N{\rChinese}是因为中国人变得富裕，把钱都存进银行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.22,English,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what happened.\N{\rChinese}不是，事情不是那样发生的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:12:01.34,English,,0,0,0,,What happened, guys? Supported by the government. Okay.\N{\rChinese}发生了什么？得到政府支持。好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:06.80,English,,0,0,0,,What happened was these banks start to lend money out to corporations,\N{\rChinese}这些银行开始向企业、政府和个人放贷。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.14,English,,0,0,0,,to government, to people,\N{\rChinese}to government, to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:13.26,English,,0,0,0,,to build skyscrapers, to build roads.\N{\rChinese}建高楼、修道路。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.74,English,,0,0,0,,In other words,\N{\rChinese}换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.34,English,,0,0,0,,the banks started to create money out\N{\rChinese}银行开始创造货币。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:23.30,English,,0,0,0,,of nothing in order to finance China's infrastructure projects.\N{\rChinese}为筹资中国基础设施项目而无中生有。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.00,English,,0,0,0,,And that's what banks are allowed to do.\N{\rChinese}这就是银行可以做的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:30.42,English,,0,0,0,,They're allowed to print money, create money out of nothing.\N{\rChinese}他们可以无中生有地印钞、造钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Does that make sense? Now the question\N{\rChinese}好的。这样说通吗？现在的问题是，等一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:38.08,English,,0,0,0,,then is, wait a minute here.\N{\rChinese}那就先等一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.72,English,,0,0,0,,That's kind of absurd. How this system come into being?\N{\rChinese}这有点荒谬。这个系统是怎么出现的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:47.10,English,,0,0,0,,How is it created? Okay. Well, actually, there's a very easy explanation for\N{\rChinese}它是怎么创建的？好的。其实有个很简单的解释，说明我们是怎么得到这个系统的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.48,English,,0,0,0,,where we got the system from.\N{\rChinese}好的。接下来让我来解释一下这个系统的历史和起源。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.42,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So let me explain the history and the origin of the system.\N{\rChinese}All right. So let me explain the history and the origin of the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.48,English,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning, it was merchants\N{\rChinese}于是最初，商人们才是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:02.16,English,,0,0,0,,who engaged in finance\N{\rChinese}他们从事金融业务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.94,English,,0,0,0,,because merchants needed money in order to facilitate trade.\N{\rChinese}因为商人需要资金来促成交易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.74,English,,0,0,0,,And some merchants became extremely wealthy.\N{\rChinese}有些商人变得极其富有。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.60,English,,0,0,0,,And when they became very wealthy,\N{\rChinese}当他们变得非常富有时，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.96,English,,0,0,0,,they started banks in order to support China.\N{\rChinese}他们便创办银行以支撑中国。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.38,English,,0,0,0,,And so they started to trade in other merchants. Okay.\N{\rChinese}于是他们开始与其他商人进行贸易。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:21.56,English,,0,0,0,,So these banks traded in gold\N{\rChinese}于是这些银行以金进行贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.00,English,,0,0,0,,because that was the primary source\N{\rChinese}因为金是主要来源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.90,English,,0,0,0,,and supply of money back then.\N{\rChinese}并在那时再补给钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:31.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So what happened is\N{\rChinese}好的。所以发生的事是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.08,English,,0,0,0,,you would come and you would put your money,\N{\rChinese}你会来，然后你会把钱放进去。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.80,English,,0,0,0,,your gold in a bank for safekeeping.\N{\rChinese}把你的黄金存入银行保管。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.54,English,,0,0,0,,And the bank would give you a contract.\N{\rChinese}银行会给你一份合同。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:46.24,English,,0,0,0,,All right. A contract is just saying,\N{\rChinese}好的。合同就是这么说，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.92,English,,0,0,0,,thank you for giving me your gold.\N{\rChinese}谢谢你给我的黄金。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:53.48,English,,0,0,0,,I promise to give back your gold at any time that you want it.\N{\rChinese}我保证随时归还你的黄金。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.60,English,,0,0,0,,And this is what we call a receipt, right?\N{\rChinese}这就是我们所说的收据，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:05.26,English,,0,0,0,,And this would allow for better\N{\rChinese}并且这将使更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.08,English,,0,0,0,,and easier trade because\N{\rChinese}而且更易交易因为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:11.94,English,,0,0,0,,now I can take this contract and I can go to England.\N{\rChinese}现在我可以拿着这份合同去英格兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Maybe I'm based in Italy, but\N{\rChinese}好的。也许我在意大利，但现在我可以去英格兰并说，听着，我需要从你那里买棉花或香蕉。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:17.66,English,,0,0,0,,now I can go to England and said, listen, I need to buy\N{\rChinese}现在我可以去英格兰并说，听着，我需要从你那里买棉花或香蕉。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:22.18,English,,0,0,0,,cotton or bananas from you.\N{\rChinese}现在我可以去英格兰并说，听着，我需要从你那里买棉花或香蕉。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.52,English,,0,0,0,,And the person was like, well, what do you give me?\N{\rChinese}于是那人说，嗯，你给我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.64,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you gold. Right.\N{\rChinese}我会给你黄金。对吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.04,English,,0,0,0,,So I take the receipt and I give it to you.\N{\rChinese}于是我拿着收据递给你。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.14,English,,0,0,0,,Right. And why do we, and why do we do this?\N{\rChinese}对了，那我们为什么要这么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.82,English,,0,0,0,,Because it's a lot easier than giving gold to other people.\N{\rChinese}因为比把黄金给别人更简单。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:41.10,English,,0,0,0,,And so this system would facilitate trade throughout the world.\N{\rChinese}这样一来，整个系统就能促进全球贸易。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:46.12,English,,0,0,0,,Does it make sense? Now I'm the bank.\N{\rChinese}它有意义吗？现在我是银行。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.58,English,,0,0,0,,I have all this gold and I want to make money with it.\N{\rChinese}我手里有这么多黄金，想靠它赚钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.54,English,,0,0,0,,So I want to give it to other people.\N{\rChinese}于是我想把它给别人。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:56.02,English,,0,0,0,,So other merchants would come to me and say, listen, I need gold.\N{\rChinese}于是其他商人会来找我说，听着，我需要黄金。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me out gold?\N{\rChinese}你能借给我黄金吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.98,English,,0,0,0,,Right. But\N{\rChinese}对了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.48,English,,0,0,0,,I say to him, yeah, but if I give you out the gold,\N{\rChinese}我对他说，好的，但如果我把黄金给你，你就有安全问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.34,English,,0,0,0,,you have a security issue.\N{\rChinese}这对你不方便。那我为什么不把黄金给你呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.08,English,,0,0,0,,It's inconvenient for you. So why don't I give you a gold?\N{\rChinese}It's inconvenient for you. Sowhy don't I give you a gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.14,English,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give me a receipt, a contract instead?\N{\rChinese}为什么不给我一张收据，一份合同呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.12,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Because all I need is a contract.\N{\rChinese}这样说对吗？因为我只需要一份合同。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.78,English,,0,0,0,,All I need is a receipt in order to go and do trade elsewhere.\N{\rChinese}我只需要一张收据，才能去别处做交易。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.32,English,,0,0,0,,Right. So, so by doing this,\N{\rChinese}好的。于是，做完这件事后，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.62,English,,0,0,0,,what I've done is I've doubled\N{\rChinese}我所做的就是把我的金子翻倍了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:34.38,English,,0,0,0,,the gold in my bank.\N{\rChinese}在我的银行里，金子翻倍了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.30,English,,0,0,0,,Right. I've created money out of nothing.\N{\rChinese}好的。我凭空创造了钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.52,English,,0,0,0,,So the gold is still 5 million.\N{\rChinese}于是，金子还是五百万。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:47.50,English,,0,0,0,,That hasn't changed, but the receipt is now 5 million plus 5 million.\N{\rChinese}那没变，但收据现在是5百万加5百万。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:53.16,English,,0,0,0,,So theoretically, I now have 10 million in the bank.\N{\rChinese}于是，理论上我现在在银行里有一千万。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So that's how money\N{\rChinese}好的，那就是这么回事。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.16,English,,0,0,0,,and finance works.\N{\rChinese}和金融运作。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.98,English,,0,0,0,,Now there's a problem with the system.\N{\rChinese}现在系统出现问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:10.22,English,,0,0,0,,What's the problem with the system? What do you mean?\N{\rChinese}系统有什么问题？你说的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.12,English,,0,0,0,,Why would he have to say the receipt has gold as the same amount of...\N{\rChinese}他为什么要说收据里有金子，和同样的金额…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. That's a good question. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的。那是个好问题。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:24.14,English,,0,0,0,,Why is it that people believe in me?\N{\rChinese}人们为什么会相信我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. The answer is very simple.\N{\rChinese}好的。答案很简单。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:30.24,English,,0,0,0,,The answer is because for most of you of human history, people didn't need money.\N{\rChinese}答案是因为在大多数人类历史里，人们不需要钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:34.52,English,,0,0,0,,If you, if you were just a normal person, what were you doing?\N{\rChinese}如果你，假设你只是普通人，你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.66,English,,0,0,0,,Were you in a village growing crops?\N{\rChinese}你是在村里种田吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.50,English,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to like get new stuff, what would you do?\N{\rChinese}如果你想买新东西，你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.10,English,,0,0,0,,You would trade with someone else, right?\N{\rChinese}你会和别人交换，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe you have a gold that I want.\N{\rChinese}也许，你手里有我想要的黄金。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.72,English,,0,0,0,,Well then I would trade you a cow for it.\N{\rChinese}那我就把一头牛换给你吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,So we didn't actually need money.\N{\rChinese}于是我们其实不需要钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.78,English,,0,0,0,,So for most of human history,\N{\rChinese}所以在大多数人类历史里，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.28,English,,0,0,0,,no one had any need for money.\N{\rChinese}没有人需要钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:58.84,English,,0,0,0,,It was only in certain circumstances that you would want money.\N{\rChinese}只有在特定情形下才会想要钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:00.48,English,,0,0,0,,So for example, marriage, right?\N{\rChinese}比如说结婚，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So for most of human history,\N{\rChinese}好的。于是在人类历史的大多数里，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.96,English,,0,0,0,,money represented...\N{\rChinese}钱代表着……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.62,English,,0,0,0,,Debt that could be unpaid.\N{\rChinese}债务永远无法偿还。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:15.68,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Debt that could never be repaid.\N{\rChinese}哦，抱歉。债务永远无法偿还。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:21.52,English,,0,0,0,,So for example, a very common thing is maybe you\N{\rChinese}比如说，一个很常见的情形是你……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.36,English,,0,0,0,,and I fight and I kill you.\N{\rChinese}我打架，我杀了你。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.24,English,,0,0,0,,Well, in theory,\N{\rChinese}好吧，理论上，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.48,English,,0,0,0,,your family should not come and kill me, but obviously that would create a lot of problems, right?\N{\rChinese}你的家族应该不会来杀我，但显然这会造成不少麻烦，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.82,English,,0,0,0,,So the way to settle the dispute is I would give your family money.\N{\rChinese}解决争端的办法是我给你家族钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.80,English,,0,0,0,,Because money was symbolically meant to say,\N{\rChinese}因为钱象征性地表示，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.66,English,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I killed you.\N{\rChinese}我很抱歉，我杀了你。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.72,English,,0,0,0,,This is a debt that can never be repaid.\N{\rChinese}这是一笔永远偿不完的债。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:50.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? That's what money was used for in most circumstances throughout human history.\N{\rChinese}对吧？这就是钱在历史上大多数情况下的用途。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.92,English,,0,0,0,,There was no actually real use for money.\N{\rChinese}钱本身并没有实际用途。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.22,English,,0,0,0,,It was symbolic. But with the rise of trade,\N{\rChinese}它是象征性的。但随着贸易的兴起，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:01.66,English,,0,0,0,,there were merchants, they needed money in order to facilitate the trade.\N{\rChinese}有商人，他们需要钱来促进贸易。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.14,English,,0,0,0,,But these merchants all knew each other.\N{\rChinese}这些商人彼此相识。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.68,English,,0,0,0,,So they trusted each other.\N{\rChinese}于是他们彼此信任。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.84,English,,0,0,0,,And they trusted each other. And they trusted each other anyway. So\N{\rChinese}他们彼此相识，彼此相信。于是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.66,English,,0,0,0,,money was a mechanism for\N{\rChinese}钱是一个机制，……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:13.02,English,,0,0,0,,them to trade easier.\N{\rChinese}让他们更容易交易。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的？那有道理吗？好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So let's go back to the question.\N{\rChinese}好的。那我们回到问题上来。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.48,English,,0,0,0,,This system looks great.\N{\rChinese}这个系统看起来不错。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.16,English,,0,0,0,,I can print money out of nothing.\N{\rChinese}我可以凭空印钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:25.04,English,,0,0,0,,But there's a problem with this system.\N{\rChinese}但这个系统有个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:29.32,English,,0,0,0,,What is the problem? There's a problem here.\N{\rChinese}问题是什么？这里有个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.32,English,,0,0,0,,Hmm?.\N{\rChinese}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:37.90,English,,0,0,0,,. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.12,English,,0,0,0,,That's actually a great question. Okay? So yeah.\N{\rChinese}这实际上是个很好的问题。好的？那就这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.30,English,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to forge the contract?\N{\rChinese}可以伪造合同吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.82,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So that's a really good point.\N{\rChinese}好的？这真是个好点子。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.70,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is...\N{\rChinese}问题是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:52.98,English,,0,0,0,,So the answer is that they all knew each other anyway.\N{\rChinese}于是答案是，他们彼此都已相识。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because it's a very small circle.\N{\rChinese}好吧？因为圈子很小。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.06,English,,0,0,0,,Again, we have not reached the modern period where\N{\rChinese}再说，我们还未到现代时期。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.76,English,,0,0,0,,it's a lot of people using money.\N{\rChinese}有很多人用钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.40,English,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then fortune becomes a problem.\N{\rChinese}如果是这样，财富就成了问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.36,English,,0,0,0,,We'll discuss this in future classes.\N{\rChinese}我们将在后续课上讨论。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Counterfeiting. But at this point in history, fortune is actually not a big issue.\N{\rChinese}好的？伪造。但在这段历史里，财富其实并不是大问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:13.80,English,,0,0,0,,There's actually a bigger issue. And it's a huge issue.\N{\rChinese}其实有更大的问题。那是个大问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.88,English,,0,0,0,,What's the issue? All right.\N{\rChinese}问题是什么？好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.52,English,,0,0,0,,$5 million of gold, right?\N{\rChinese}$500万的黄金，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:24.14,English,,0,0,0,,There's about $10 million of gold out there in receipts.\N{\rChinese}大约有1000万的黄金在收据里。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.90,English,,0,0,0,,What's the problem with that?.\N{\rChinese}那有什么问题呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:32.62,English,,0,0,0,,. The problem is that if everyone wants the gold at the same time,\N{\rChinese}问题是如果大家同时想要黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.50,English,,0,0,0,,I go bankrupt, right?\N{\rChinese}我破产了，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:39.08,English,,0,0,0,,Because I lose my reputation. The contract says that\N{\rChinese}因为我失去声誉。合同写着这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:42.74,English,,0,0,0,,at any time you want the gold, I must give it to you.\N{\rChinese}在任何你想要黄金的时刻，我必须交给你。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.52,English,,0,0,0,,But if I have like...\N{\rChinese}但如果我有……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.70,English,,0,0,0,,If there's $100 million in gold contracts,\N{\rChinese}如果有一亿美元的黄金合约，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.52,English,,0,0,0,,but I only have $10 million in gold,\N{\rChinese}但我只有一千万美元的黄金。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:56.48,English,,0,0,0,,only if $15 million wants the gold back,\N{\rChinese}只有当1,500万美元想要黄金时，我才会被搞砸。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.32,English,,0,0,0,,then I'm screwed. This is what we call a bank run.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们所说的银行挤兑。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? A bank run. And\N{\rChinese}好的？银行挤兑。还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.10,English,,0,0,0,,this is a huge problem for merchants.\N{\rChinese}这对商人来说是个大问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:12.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? There's also another problem with this system.\N{\rChinese}好的？这个系统还有另一个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:16.84,English,,0,0,0,,And the problem is this. Who\N{\rChinese}问题是这样的。谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.26,English,,0,0,0,,do I usually lend my money to?\N{\rChinese}我通常把钱借给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.10,English,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know? If I'm a bank, if I'm a merchant, who do I usually lend my money to?\N{\rChinese}你们知道吗？如果我是银行，如果我是商人，我通常把钱借给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.54,English,,0,0,0,,. Okay, guys.\N{\rChinese}好的，大家。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,Today, we lend the money to our subscribers.\N{\rChinese}今天，我们把钱借给我们的订阅者。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.64,English,,0,0,0,,Ubuntu.\N{\rChinese}Ubuntu。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.28,English,,0,0,0,,the king would be like,\N{\rChinese}国王会是这样，像是……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.56,English,,0,0,0,,screw you bank, I don't need to pay you back.\N{\rChinese}把你们的银行搞砸，我不需要还钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:08.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So there's actually a lot of risk with this system.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以这个系统实际上有很多风险。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,So over time,\N{\rChinese}于是，随着时间的推移，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:14.78,English,,0,0,0,,develop a system to mitigate or reduce this risk.\N{\rChinese}他们会发展出一种系统来缓解或降低这种风险。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:19.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? What they would do is they would create cartels.\N{\rChinese}他们会做的就是创建卡特尔。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.26,English,,0,0,0,,Cartels are just partnerships.\N{\rChinese}卡特尔只是合作关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.32,English,,0,0,0,,So maybe this bank works with another bank,\N{\rChinese}所以这家银行可能与另一家银行合作，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.12,English,,0,0,0,,works with another bank throughout Europe.\N{\rChinese}在整个欧洲与另一家银行合作。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.58,English,,0,0,0,,And the way they establish these cartels is usually through intermarriage, right?\N{\rChinese}他们通过联姻来建立这些卡特尔，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.52,English,,0,0,0,,They would marry each other. They would combine together.\N{\rChinese}他们互相结婚，合并在一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.14,English,,0,0,0,,And that way,\N{\rChinese}于是这样，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.84,English,,0,0,0,,let's say 15\N{\rChinese}让我们说15
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:45.62,English,,0,0,0,,million of receipts wants back the gold,\N{\rChinese}百万收据想要回金子，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.94,English,,0,0,0,,but there's only 10 million. Well, guess what?\N{\rChinese}但只有10百万。好吧，猜猜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.34,English,,0,0,0,,You just go to another bank. Okay?\N{\rChinese}你只要去另一家银行。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:51.24,English,,0,0,0,,And let's just say a king.\N{\rChinese}再说一个国王。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.14,English,,0,0,0,,Decides, I'm not going to pay you back, bank. Well,\N{\rChinese}决定，我不再还钱给你，银行。好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:58.86,English,,0,0,0,,your bank works with other banks to establish a new\N{\rChinese}你的银行与其他银行合作，建立一个新的敌人，去杀掉国王以取回钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.56,English,,0,0,0,,enemy to kill the king to get the money back.\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.96,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? And\N{\rChinese}Do you understand? And
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,this system is what we call today central banking.\N{\rChinese}这个系统就是我们今天所说的中央银行制度。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:17.46,English,,0,0,0,,And what you will learn in this class is central banking controls the world today.\N{\rChinese}在这门课里你会学到，中央银行控制着今天的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:23.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now,\N{\rChinese}好了？现在，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.10,English,,0,0,0,,what's really important about this system is\N{\rChinese}这套系统真正重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:30.24,English,,0,0,0,,that it's based on power.\N{\rChinese}它是基于力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? And what power is, you can turn nothing,\N{\rChinese}对吧？而力量是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:40.30,English,,0,0,0,,money, the contract into everything.\N{\rChinese}钱，合同融入一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.00,English,,0,0,0,,Right? That's what money is.\N{\rChinese}对吧？这就是钱的意义。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. So we live in a world in\N{\rChinese}好了。好了。我们生活在一个世界里。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:52.18,English,,0,0,0,,which banks can print out money.\N{\rChinese}哪家银行可以印出钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:55.34,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So now let's ask ourselves the question.\N{\rChinese}对吧？现在让我们自己问个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:57.30,English,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute here.\N{\rChinese}等一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:02.46,English,,0,0,0,,If the banks can print as much money as possible,\N{\rChinese}如果银行可以印出尽可能多的钱，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:07.00,English,,0,0,0,,why do we have poverty?\N{\rChinese}那为什么我们还有贫困？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:14.74,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Because we can just give money to poor people and they wouldn't be poor anymore.\N{\rChinese}对吧？因为我们可以把钱给穷人，他们就不再贫困了。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:22.04,English,,0,0,0,,Why do we have poverty? Because we can just give money to poor people and they wouldn't be poor anymore.\N{\rChinese}为什么我们还有贫困？因为我们可以把钱给穷人，他们就不再贫困了。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:25.48,English,,0,0,0,,Because we can just give money to poor people and they wouldn't be poor anymore. the world that we want, why are people starving still?\N{\rChinese}因为我们可以把钱给穷人，他们就不再贫困了。我们想要的世界，为什么人们仍在挨饿？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:31.96,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Okay.\N{\rChinese}为什么？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.68,English,,0,0,0,,So we don't have limited resources.\N{\rChinese}于是我们就没有有限资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.40,English,,0,0,0,,We have scarcity. Okay. Right.\N{\rChinese}我们有稀缺。好的。对。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:39.60,English,,0,0,0,,So that is the common answer.\N{\rChinese}所以这就是常见答案。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:41.10,English,,0,0,0,,Scarcity. We have poverty\N{\rChinese}稀缺。我们有贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:45.74,English,,0,0,0,,because of scarcity, but I already told you this.\N{\rChinese}因为稀缺，但我已经告诉你了。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.50,English,,0,0,0,,They can print money out of nothing.\N{\rChinese}他们可以凭空印钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:49.80,English,,0,0,0,,So money is infinite.\N{\rChinese}钱是无限的。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:51.84,English,,0,0,0,,Money is an infinite resource.\N{\rChinese}钱是一种无限资源。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:57.62,English,,0,0,0,,So why are we, why do we have poor people then? That's kind of strange.\N{\rChinese}那为什么我们会有贫困的人呢？这有点奇怪。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:11.80,English,,0,0,0,,You see\N{\rChinese}你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.18,English,,0,0,0,,what's happening is this.\N{\rChinese}正在发生的事就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:16.22,English,,0,0,0,,You all believe money is scarce.\N{\rChinese}你们都认为钱是稀缺的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:19.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. I just spent the past 10, 20 minutes explaining to you.\N{\rChinese}好的。好的。我刚刚用十、二十分钟解释给你听。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.44,English,,0,0,0,,It's not scarce. It's infinite.\N{\rChinese}它不是稀缺的，它是无限的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:26.62,English,,0,0,0,,It's just a number. We can at any time print out as much money as we need.\N{\rChinese}它只是一个数字。我们随时可以印出所需的金额。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So that's how power works.\N{\rChinese}好的。那就是权力的运作方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.58,0:24:33.20,English,,0,0,0,,Power has brainwashed you into thinking something\N{\rChinese}权力让你脑中装上了一个不真实的想法。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:34.40,English,,0,0,0,,that is not true.\N{\rChinese}这想法并不是真的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.92,0:24:37.72,English,,0,0,0,,You've been taught from the first day\N{\rChinese}从第一天起你就被教导，钱是稀缺的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.72,0:24:41.18,English,,0,0,0,,that money is scarce,\N{\rChinese}that money is scarce,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:43.94,English,,0,0,0,,but it's not scarce.\N{\rChinese}但它并不稀缺。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:47.48,English,,0,0,0,,It's infinite. And no matter what I say to you, it's not true.\N{\rChinese}它是无限的。无论我对你说什么，都是不对的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:48.90,English,,0,0,0,,It's not true. It's not true. It's not true. It's not true. It's not true. You still believe this. Okay.\N{\rChinese}它是这样才对的。它是这样才对的。它是这样才对的。它是这样才对的。它是这样才对的。你仍然相信。好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:51.56,English,,0,0,0,,So you have to get that out of your head.\N{\rChinese}于是你得把它从脑子里拿出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:53.20,English,,0,0,0,,Money is not scarce. It is infinite.\N{\rChinese}钱并不稀缺，它是无限的。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.38,0:24:54.84,English,,0,0,0,,So let's work with a question.\N{\rChinese}于是我们用一个问题来展开。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:58.10,English,,0,0,0,,Why is there poverty in this world?\N{\rChinese}为什么世界上有贫穷？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:25:02.12,English,,0,0,0,,Why do people starve? Why is there inequality in this world?\N{\rChinese}为什么人们会挨饿？为什么世界上会有不平等？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:04.96,English,,0,0,0,,Why are there poor people? Why are there rich people?\N{\rChinese}为什么有穷人？为什么有富人？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:09.70,English,,0,0,0,,What's the answer? Because\N{\rChinese}答案是什么？因为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:13.28,English,,0,0,0,,they don't print. Okay.\N{\rChinese}他们没印出来。好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.28,0:25:15.08,English,,0,0,0,,Because it's scarce.\N{\rChinese}因为它很稀缺。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.26,0:25:16.76,English,,0,0,0,,So guys, this is amazing.\N{\rChinese}所以各位，这太精彩了。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:18.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. You guys can't get it out of your head.\N{\rChinese}好的，你们想不出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:20.56,English,,0,0,0,,You think money's scarce.\N{\rChinese}你认为货币稀缺。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.88,0:25:23.98,English,,0,0,0,,You think it is not possible to print infinite money\N{\rChinese}你认为可以印无限货币。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.98,0:25:28.16,English,,0,0,0,,when I already told you it is possible to print infinite money because they do this all the time.\N{\rChinese}当我已经告诉你可以印无限货币，因为他们一直这么做。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:31.42,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah? The one who\N{\rChinese}是吗？那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.42,0:25:36.12,English,,0,0,0,,has the power don't want everyone to share the same...\N{\rChinese}有权力的人不想让大家共享同样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:44.40,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because we don't want people to all have money.\N{\rChinese}是的，因为我们不想让大家都有钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.40,0:25:47.26,English,,0,0,0,,The powerful people don't want that.\N{\rChinese}强者不想这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.44,0:25:49.32,English,,0,0,0,,That's the exact answer. And why?\N{\rChinese}这就是答案。为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:54.98,English,,0,0,0,,Because otherwise no one would work. Do you understand?\N{\rChinese}否则没人会工作。你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:26:00.44,English,,0,0,0,,The point of printing money is not to give you money.\N{\rChinese}印钱的要点不是给你钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.56,0:26:04.62,English,,0,0,0,,The point of printing money is to create the illusion\N{\rChinese}印钱的要点是制造一种幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,that money is valuable and therefore\N{\rChinese}钱才是有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:11.50,English,,0,0,0,,you work hard in order to obtain it.\N{\rChinese}你努力工作以获得它。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:14.38,English,,0,0,0,,But in order for me to make money,\N{\rChinese}但为了让我赚钱，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.38,0:26:16.06,English,,0,0,0,,to make you want to get money,\N{\rChinese}让你想要得到钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,I need to create artificial misery.\N{\rChinese}我需要制造人为的痛苦。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.54,0:26:24.86,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Right?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.24,0:26:28.26,English,,0,0,0,,If there weren't poor people, you wouldn't want to be rich.\N{\rChinese}如果没有穷人，你就不会想要富裕。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:33.16,English,,0,0,0,,It's only because you see people suffer that you would want to go make money for yourself.\N{\rChinese}只有看到人们受苦，你才会想为自己赚钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.10,0:26:37.50,English,,0,0,0,,What do your parents tell you? Your parents tell you work hard in school, make a lot of money.\N{\rChinese}你父母会说：努力读书，赚大钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.66,0:26:40.20,English,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're gonna end up like a poor person.\N{\rChinese}不然你就会像穷人一样。”
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Well, guess what?\N{\rChinese}对吧？那你猜怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:45.18,English,,0,0,0,,If there are no poor people, your parents couldn't say that to you.\N{\rChinese}如果没有穷人，你父母就不会这么说。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:47.16,English,,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't want to work hard in school.\N{\rChinese}你也就不会想在学校努力读书。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.32,0:26:51.78,English,,0,0,0,,Right? That's why we have poverty.\N{\rChinese}对吧？这就是我们有贫困的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:56.52,English,,0,0,0,,Because poverty creates the illusion that money is valuable.\N{\rChinese}因为贫困让人们产生钱才有价值的错觉。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.62,0:27:05.68,English,,0,0,0,,In other words, poverty isn't what you do to yourself,\N{\rChinese}换句话说，贫困不是你对自己的所作所为。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.02,0:27:07.66,English,,0,0,0,,it is what the powerful do to you.\N{\rChinese}它是强者对你的所作所为。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.22,0:27:12.44,English,,0,0,0,,Now let me ask you another question.\N{\rChinese}现在让我再问你一个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.44,0:27:14.02,English,,0,0,0,,You guys have studied some economics.\N{\rChinese}你们已经学过一些经济学了。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.46,0:27:16.10,English,,0,0,0,,Why do you have like crises?\N{\rChinese}为什么你们会出现危机？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.76,0:27:22.32,English,,0,0,0,,Crises. For example, there's a stock market crash.\N{\rChinese}危机。例如，股市崩盘。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.90,0:27:25.94,English,,0,0,0,,Or for example, the economy goes down and people lose their jobs.\N{\rChinese}或者说，经济下行，人们失业。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.12,0:27:31.06,English,,0,0,0,,Why do you have crises? I don't think.\N{\rChinese}为什么你们会出现危机？我想不通。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.36,0:27:33.22,English,,0,0,0,,Exactly. You're not taught this in economics class.\N{\rChinese}完全正确。你们在经济课上没学过。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:38.24,English,,0,0,0,,That's kind of weird, right? The point of crises is to destroy money.\N{\rChinese}这有点奇怪，吧？危机的要点是毁钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.92,0:27:42.42,English,,0,0,0,,Why do we need to destroy money? Because if there's too much money in the stock market,\N{\rChinese}为什么我们要销毁钱？因为如果股市里钱太多，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.42,0:27:44.00,English,,0,0,0,,in the system, people don't have to work.\N{\rChinese}系统里人就不必工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.46,0:27:49.74,English,,0,0,0,,So you have to destroy this money in order to make people feel money is scarce.\N{\rChinese}于是你们就得销毁钱，让人们觉得钱稀缺。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.58,0:27:55.92,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? So why do we have wars?\N{\rChinese}好的，听得懂吗？那为什么我们会有战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.54,0:27:59.06,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Why are there wars in the world then?\N{\rChinese}对吧？那世界上为什么会有战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:03.44,English,,0,0,0,,Because they're fighting over scarce resources, right?\N{\rChinese}因为他们在争夺稀缺资源，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.08,0:28:06.52,English,,0,0,0,,I already told you. Scarcity is a lie.\N{\rChinese}我已经告诉你了。稀缺是谎言。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.72,0:28:10.00,English,,0,0,0,,The real reason is war is meant to destroy wealth.\N{\rChinese}真正的原因是战争是用来消灭财富的。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:15.04,English,,0,0,0,,In order to make you think money is valuable.\N{\rChinese}让你们觉得钱有价值。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.68,0:28:19.90,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? You guys play World of Warcraft?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？你们玩《魔兽世界》吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.48,0:28:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,Or these games, right? Guess what, guys?\N{\rChinese}或者玩这些游戏，对吧？猜猜看，伙计们？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.18,0:28:26.02,English,,0,0,0,,World of Warcraft, in our world, there's actually no difference.\N{\rChinese}《魔兽世界》在我们世界里，其实无二者。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.28,0:28:30.96,English,,0,0,0,,You just run around pointlessly, working hard to obtain credits in order to buy stuff.\N{\rChinese}你只是在无目的地跑来跑去，努力赚取积分以买东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.32,0:28:34.06,English,,0,0,0,,If credits just flew out of the sky, because they could do that, right?\N{\rChinese}如果积分能从天上掉下来，因为他们可以做到，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:37.64,English,,0,0,0,,They could actually program the engine to just put money out of nothing,\N{\rChinese}他们实际上可以把引擎编程成随便生成积分。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:39.52,English,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't do nothing every day.\N{\rChinese}你每天都不会什么都不做。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.56,0:28:41.68,English,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't play the game. Right?\N{\rChinese}你不会玩游戏。对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.68,0:28:44.50,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? It's only because you believe\N{\rChinese}好吧？只是因为你相信。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.50,0:28:47.44,English,,0,0,0,,that there's scarcity in the world\N{\rChinese}世界上有稀缺，必须努力工作才能获得财富。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.44,0:28:49.92,English,,0,0,0,,and that you must work hard to obtain wealth\N{\rChinese}你必须努力工作才能得到财富。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.02,0:28:55.24,English,,0,0,0,,that you do any work. Do you understand this?\N{\rChinese}你做任何工作都要努力。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.20,0:28:58.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So this world that we live in,\N{\rChinese}好的？我们生活的这个世界，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:28:59.84,English,,0,0,0,,it's a complete illusion\N{\rChinese}它是完全的幻觉，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.54,0:29:04.44,English,,0,0,0,,created by central banking in order to\N{\rChinese}由中央银行创造的，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.44,0:29:06.66,English,,0,0,0,,make us work as hard as possible.\N{\rChinese}让我们尽可能努力工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.08,0:29:08.96,English,,0,0,0,,Because the real value is not money.\N{\rChinese}因为真正的价值不在于金钱。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:16.18,English,,0,0,0,,The real value is the work we do. There's only\N{\rChinese}真正的价值是我们所做的工作。
