Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.54,0:55:30.10,English,,0,0,0,,that I'm going to give you some history okay\N{\rChinese}我会给你讲一些历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.64,0:55:33.94,English,,0,0,0,,we will do a lot of history in this class but\N{\rChinese}我们在这节课里会做很多历史。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.94,0:55:36.80,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you the three societies that\N{\rChinese}我要给你讲三个最早实行义务教育的社会
