Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.62,0:57:04.36,English,,0,0,0,,okay War War\N{\rChinese}好了，战争，战争
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.90,0:57:09.60,English,,0,0,0,,War War War War War War War War War War War War War War\N{\rChinese}战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.18,0:57:13.02,English,,0,0,0,,War War War War War War War War War War War War War War War\N{\rChinese}战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争，战争
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.60,0:57:30.86,English,,0,0,0,,War War right?\N{\rChinese}战争，战争，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.14,0:57:33.82,English,,0,0,0,,It's the Spartan warrior. Okay?\N{\rChinese}那是斯巴达战士。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.42,0:57:38.76,English,,0,0,0,,The Aztecs were the greatest\N{\rChinese}阿兹特克人是中美洲最伟大的战争社会
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.76,0:57:42.78,English,,0,0,0,,war society in Central America before the arrival of the Europeans.\N{\rChinese}在欧洲人到来之前的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.24,0:57:44.52,English,,0,0,0,,They defeated everyone.\N{\rChinese}他们击败了所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.94,0:57:46.80,English,,0,0,0,,They were engaged in war.\N{\rChinese}他们也在战争中投入。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.10,0:57:49.10,English,,0,0,0,,They also did a lot of human sacrifice as well.\N{\rChinese}他们也做了大量人祭。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.46,0:57:51.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, we learn about the Aztecs later on.\N{\rChinese}好的，稍后我们再学习阿兹特克人。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.02,0:57:54.40,English,,0,0,0,,Prussia, the Prussians,\N{\rChinese}普鲁士，普鲁士人，
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.48,0:57:57.62,English,,0,0,0,,the greatest military in Europe for centuries.\N{\rChinese}在欧洲数百年里是最强大的军队。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.08,0:58:01.92,English,,0,0,0,,They were engaged in war making as well.\N{\rChinese}他们也从事战争制造。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.52,0:58:03.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, do you understand this?\N{\rChinese}好的，你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.48,0:58:07.24,English,,0,0,0,,Why we have schools is because schools\N{\rChinese}我们有学校的原因是因为学校
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.92,0:58:13.76,English,,0,0,0,,are really good at preparing people for war.\N{\rChinese}学校真的很擅长把人准备好去打仗。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.02,0:58:19.68,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Excuse me?\N{\rChinese}为什么？请问一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.46,0:58:29.60,English,,0,0,0,,What is, what is, why, why?\N{\rChinese}什么，什么，为什么，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.68,0:58:33.24,English,,0,0,0,,Let me, Let me ask you this question. Why did they not have schools before?\N{\rChinese}让我，先问你一个问题。为什么他们以前没有学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.86,0:58:36.08,English,,0,0,0,,Why is it that people were like, we don't want schools, why?\N{\rChinese}为什么人们会说我们不想要学校，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.40,0:58:41.28,English,,0,0,0,,Again, the exporter, assets and\N{\rChinese}再说一次，出口商、资产和……
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.28,0:58:45.16,English,,0,0,0,,pressure were the few societies that had free public schooling.\N{\rChinese}压力是少数拥有免费公立学校的社会。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.18,0:58:48.64,English,,0,0,0,,Why didn't other societies just copy them?\N{\rChinese}为什么其他社会没有直接复制它们？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.06,0:58:54.94,English,,0,0,0,,Why? In order to be trained with mind.\N{\rChinese}为什么？为了用心灵训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.26,0:58:57.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me ask you this question. Let's just say you're a mother or father.\N{\rChinese}好了，我来问你个问题。假设你是父母。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.80,0:58:59.80,English,,0,0,0,,And you have a child, right?\N{\rChinese}你有个孩子，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.90,0:59:02.40,English,,0,0,0,,What's the worst thing that could happen in your life?\N{\rChinese}你生命中最糟糕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.36,0:59:09.30,English,,0,0,0,,No parents? No, no, your mother or your father.\N{\rChinese}没有父母？不不不，是你的母亲或父亲。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.58,0:59:10.86,English,,0,0,0,,You have a child, right?\N{\rChinese}你有个孩子，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.96,0:59:14.26,English,,0,0,0,,What's the worst thing that can happen to you in your life?\N{\rChinese}你生命中最糟糕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.34,0:59:19.12,English,,0,0,0,,Your child is taken away from you, right?\N{\rChinese}你的孩子被带走了，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.82,0:59:20.82,English,,0,0,0,,What does school do?\N{\rChinese}学校做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.38,0:59:30.24,English,,0,0,0,,School is designed to take your child away from you,\N{\rChinese}学校的设计是把孩子从你身边带走，
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.38,0:59:34.30,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Let me ask you this question.\N{\rChinese}好了，我来问你个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.42,0:59:40.08,English,,0,0,0,,If school is about learning, why don't parents and children go to school together?\N{\rChinese}如果学校是学习的事，为什么父母和孩子不一起去学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.58,0:59:42.84,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not?\N{\rChinese}是啊，为什么不呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.12,0:59:45.80,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Because they have to work to survive.\N{\rChinese}因为他们得工作才能维持生计。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.24,0:59:50.50,English,,0,0,0,,Because parents have to work to survive, right?\N{\rChinese}因为父母得工作才能维持生计，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.74,0:59:52.00,English,,0,0,0,,There's actually a better reason why.\N{\rChinese}实际上还有更好的理由。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.68,0:59:55.20,English,,0,0,0,,School is compromised in the social.\N{\rChinese}学校在社会层面已被打破。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.44,0:59:57.52,English,,0,0,0,,They must have two people to do something.\N{\rChinese}他们必须有两个人来完成这件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.64,0:59:59.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's about brainwashing, right?\N{\rChinese}好的，主要是脑洗，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.54,1:00:02.14,English,,0,0,0,,Because how do you brainwash someone?\N{\rChinese}那你怎么把人脑洗呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.48,1:00:05.10,English,,0,0,0,,They're too old to talk to. Right?\N{\rChinese}他们太老了，没法再聊，吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.50,1:00:08.94,English,,0,0,0,,If you're with your parent, are you gonna be brainwashed?\N{\rChinese}如果你和父母在一起，你会被洗脑吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.68,1:00:11.36,English,,0,0,0,,No, because you feel loved.\N{\rChinese}不，因为你感到被爱。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.44,1:00:13.34,English,,0,0,0,,You feel secure. Your parents are gonna protect you.\N{\rChinese}你会觉得安全。父母会保护你。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.40,1:00:17.18,English,,0,0,0,,You're gonna ask your parent, hey, is this teacher, is he or she lying to me?\N{\rChinese}你会问父母，嘿，这位老师，他/她在跟我说谎吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.30,1:00:19.36,English,,0,0,0,,And the parent's like, yeah, he's lying to you, okay?\N{\rChinese}父母会说，嗯，他在跟你说谎，好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.34,1:00:22.86,English,,0,0,0,,It's only because you've been taken away from your parent\N{\rChinese}只是因为你被从父母身边带走，才会愿意被洗脑。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.86,1:00:27.26,English,,0,0,0,,that you are now willing to be brainwashed.\N{\rChinese}为什么？因为离开父母后会发生什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.38,1:00:30.04,English,,0,0,0,,Why? Because what happens if you leave your parents?\N{\rChinese}Why? Because what happensif you leave your parents?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.18,1:00:32.86,English,,0,0,0,,How do you feel? How do you feel?\N{\rChinese}你感觉怎样？你感觉怎样？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.06,1:00:35.40,English,,0,0,0,,Insecure. Insecure.\N{\rChinese}不安。不安。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.68,1:00:38.54,English,,0,0,0,,Insecure. Yeah, exactly, right?\N{\rChinese}不安。对，正是如此，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.22,1:00:40.82,English,,0,0,0,,Insecure. You're anxious.\N{\rChinese}不安。你焦虑。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.94,1:00:44.30,English,,0,0,0,,You're afraid. You understand?\N{\rChinese}你害怕。你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.96,1:00:48.28,English,,0,0,0,,You've lost your parent. You're four, you're five, you're six years old.\N{\rChinese}你失去父母。你四岁、五岁、六岁。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.34,1:00:51.04,English,,0,0,0,,You've lost your parent. You feel really insecure.\N{\rChinese}你失去父母，感觉很不安。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.84,1:00:53.24,English,,0,0,0,,So who do you trust?\N{\rChinese}那么你信任谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.80,1:00:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,Teacher. Your teacher. What if your teacher says, is now correct?\N{\rChinese}老师。你的老师。假如老师说，才是正确的？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.94,1:01:01.66,English,,0,0,0,,One of our parents is also brainwashed.\N{\rChinese}我们的父母之一也被洗脑了。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.02,1:01:05.78,English,,0,0,0,,Because they went to school before when they were school.\N{\rChinese}因为他们以前上学时就去过学校。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.78,1:01:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, that's a great point, okay?\N{\rChinese}好，好的，这点很不错，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.74,1:01:09.66,English,,0,0,0,,Aren't our parents brainwashed as well?\N{\rChinese}我们的父母也被洗脑了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.96,1:01:13.86,English,,0,0,0,,That's correct. Your parents are brainwashed.\N{\rChinese}没错。你的父母被洗脑了。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.96,1:01:18.56,English,,0,0,0,,But what I'm saying is, when a parent is with a child, the child feels secure.\N{\rChinese}我说的是，父母在孩子身边时，孩子会觉得安全。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.96,1:01:22.84,English,,0,0,0,,And if you're secure, you're much more willing to disobey authority.\N{\rChinese}如果你感到安全，你就更愿意不服从命。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.38,1:01:25.26,English,,0,0,0,,You're much willing to ask questions.\N{\rChinese}你更愿意提问问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.26,1:01:28.02,English,,0,0,0,,You're much willing to think for yourself.\N{\rChinese}你更愿意自我思考。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.38,1:01:31.14,English,,0,0,0,,Because you feel secure. Because your parent is there to protect you.\N{\rChinese}因为你感到安全。因为父母在身边保护你。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.40,1:01:33.84,English,,0,0,0,,But if you take the parent away, you can't do that.\N{\rChinese}但如果把父母移走，你就做不到这件事。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.22,1:01:37.84,English,,0,0,0,,You must now rely on the teacher, who can now brainwash you.\N{\rChinese}你现在必须靠老师，老师就能把你洗脑。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.96,1:01:41.24,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So are you brainwashing us?\N{\rChinese}好的？那你们在洗脑吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.36,1:01:44.62,English,,0,0,0,,Am I brainwashing you? Okay.\N{\rChinese}我在洗脑你吗？好的。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.68,1:01:47.06,English,,0,0,0,,It's a job too. Okay, all right.\N{\rChinese}这也是一份工作。好的，全部完成。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.28,1:01:50.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the question is, am I brainwashing you?\N{\rChinese}好的，那问题是，我在洗脑你吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.14,1:01:51.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a good question.\N{\rChinese}好的，这是个不错的问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.58,1:01:53.90,English,,0,0,0,,And it's a fair question. And again,\N{\rChinese}而且这是个合理的问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.34,1:01:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,that's why I tell you this.\N{\rChinese}这就是我告诉你的原因。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.98,1:01:59.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? You have the capacity to ask me questions.\N{\rChinese}好吧？你有能力向我提问。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.90,1:02:02.00,English,,0,0,0,,You have the capacity to challenge me.\N{\rChinese}你有能力来挑战我。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.42,1:02:04.76,English,,0,0,0,,You have the capacity to think for yourself.\N{\rChinese}你有能力自己思考。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.86,1:02:08.54,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So all I'm saying is, hear me out,\N{\rChinese}好吧？所以我说的只是，先听我说，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.12,1:02:12.92,English,,0,0,0,,ask me questions, and then think for yourself whether or not I make sense.\N{\rChinese}问我问题，然后自己思考我说的是否有道理。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.72,1:02:17.32,English,,0,0,0,,Because the difference between my class and other classes is like, I don't test you.\N{\rChinese}因为我的班级和其他班级的区别在于，我不做测验。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.84,1:02:20.14,English,,0,0,0,,Right? I don't give you grades. It's a pass -fail class.\N{\rChinese}对吧？我不给你成绩。是及格-不及格的班级。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.26,1:02:23.88,English,,0,0,0,,You can actually choose to say, you know what?\N{\rChinese}你实际上可以选择说，你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.90,1:02:26.62,English,,0,0,0,,This is nonsense. I don't want to listen anymore.\N{\rChinese}这没道理。我不想再听了。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.20,1:02:28.58,English,,0,0,0,,I can't stop you.\N{\rChinese}我没法停住你。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.26,1:02:32.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But in school, guess what happens if you don't come to school?\N{\rChinese}好吧？但在学校，猜猜如果你不去上学会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.70,1:02:37.14,English,,0,0,0,,Your parents get arrested. All right?\N{\rChinese}你的父母被逮捕。好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.48,1:02:39.70,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? That's the difference.\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？这就是区别。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.16,1:02:43.78,English,,0,0,0,,It's your choice whether or not to pay attention or not.\N{\rChinese}你是否注意到，是否不注意，都是你的选择。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.36,1:02:49.30,English,,0,0,0,,All right. So now the question is, okay,\N{\rChinese}好的。现在问题是，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.36,1:02:53.88,English,,0,0,0,,if schools are designed to bring you in,\N{\rChinese}如果学校是为了把你拉进去，
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.88,1:02:56.02,English,,0,0,0,,to brainwash you, what are they brainwashing you in?\N{\rChinese}洗脑，你们被洗脑成什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.54,1:02:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,Well, they're designed to brainwash you to believe a concept\N{\rChinese}好吧，他们是为了洗脑你，让你相信一个概念
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.12,1:03:01.46,English,,0,0,0,,called the nation state.\N{\rChinese}叫做民族国家。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.28,1:03:06.34,English,,0,0,0,,The nation state.\N{\rChinese}民族国家。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.96,1:03:13.80,English,,0,0,0,,The schools are designed to brainwash you to think the nation state exists.\N{\rChinese}学校是为了洗脑你，让你认为民族国家存在。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.22,1:03:16.42,English,,0,0,0,,It is a person, mother China.\N{\rChinese}它是一个人，母亲中国。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.96,1:03:18.66,English,,0,0,0,,You must love this person.\N{\rChinese}你必须爱这个人。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.76,1:03:21.02,English,,0,0,0,,You must be willing to sacrifice yourself for this person.\N{\rChinese}你必须愿意为这人牺牲自己。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.22,1:03:25.54,English,,0,0,0,,You must be willing to take it yourself, to this person, because it is mother China.\N{\rChinese}你必须愿意为这人承担，因它是母亲中国。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.20,1:03:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,And how do we brainwash you?\N{\rChinese}我们怎么洗脑你？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.76,1:03:29.46,English,,0,0,0,,We teach you language, right?\N{\rChinese}我们教你语言，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.84,1:03:31.32,English,,0,0,0,,We teach you history.\N{\rChinese}我们教你历史。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.74,1:03:33.06,English,,0,0,0,,We teach you geography.\N{\rChinese}我们教你地理。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.98,1:03:36.74,English,,0,0,0,,We teach you all this to make you believe\N{\rChinese}我们把这一切教给你，让你相信
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.74,1:03:39.56,English,,0,0,0,,that the nation state, mother China,\N{\rChinese}那民族国家，母亲中国，
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.74,1:03:42.24,English,,0,0,0,,the United States, France, they all exist.\N{\rChinese}美国、法国，它们都…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.66,1:03:45.82,English,,0,0,0,,But guess what? For most of human history,\N{\rChinese}但你猜怎么了？在大部分人类历史里，
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.64,1:03:50.04,English,,0,0,0,,it was absurd to think the nation state existed.\N{\rChinese}它荒诞地认为民族国家存在。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.00,1:03:52.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Before,\N{\rChinese}好的？之前，
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.42,1:03:56.08,English,,0,0,0,,I'm Chinese. Before you say, I'm a Beijing -er.\N{\rChinese}我就是中国人。你说我来自北京。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.84,1:03:58.96,English,,0,0,0,,Or I'm from Hai Dian.\N{\rChinese}或者我来自海淼。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.50,1:04:00.88,English,,0,0,0,,Or I'm from Chaoyang, right?\N{\rChinese}或者我来自朝阳，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.14,1:04:02.38,English,,0,0,0,,Because that makes more sense.\N{\rChinese}因为这样更有道理。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.32,1:04:05.94,English,,0,0,0,,You're from a place where you know the people.\N{\rChinese}你来自一个你了解人们的地方。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.50,1:04:10.02,English,,0,0,0,,But now, because of the nation state, you are forced to believe\N{\rChinese}但现在，因为民族国家，你被迫相信
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.02,1:04:13.84,English,,0,0,0,,that you are the same person as someone from Yunnan,\N{\rChinese}你和云南人是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.44,1:04:16.36,English,,0,0,0,,Tibet, Guangxi.\N{\rChinese}你和藏人、广西人是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.56,1:04:20.04,English,,0,0,0,,Even though, guess what guys, you have absolutely nothing in common.\N{\rChinese}即便如此，猜猜吧，伙计们，你们完全没有共同点。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.40,1:04:23.40,English,,0,0,0,,But you're all Chinese. And that's what school is designed to do.\N{\rChinese}但你们都是中国人。正是学校的设计所做的事。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.42,1:04:26.52,English,,0,0,0,,School is designed to implant in\N{\rChinese}学校的设计是为了植入
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.52,1:04:31.32,English,,0,0,0,,you a false memory of a nation state.\N{\rChinese}你是民族国家的虚假记忆。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.76,1:04:33.12,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's what history is.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是历史。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.20,1:04:35.82,English,,0,0,0,,History is the false memory of a nation state.\N{\rChinese}历史是民族国家的虚假记忆。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.34,1:04:41.38,English,,0,0,0,,And it happens. And\N{\rChinese}于是就发生了。然后
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.38,1:04:43.82,English,,0,0,0,,that's why you're all forced to go to school.\N{\rChinese}这就是你们被迫去上学的原因。
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.86,1:04:49.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Maybe,\N{\rChinese}好的？也许，
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.42,1:04:51.94,English,,0,0,0,,like, we also want you to just,\N{\rChinese}像，我们也想让你只，
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.02,1:04:56.34,English,,0,0,0,,you know, think about degrees and work as a normal person,\N{\rChinese}你知道，想想学位和工作，像个普通人一样，
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.44,1:04:59.76,English,,0,0,0,,not to create a people business or live by yourself.\N{\rChinese}不必为人民事务而生。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.08,1:05:01.64,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So, yeah. So,\N{\rChinese}是的。于是，嗯。于是，
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.70,1:05:05.06,English,,0,0,0,,the point of school is to serve the nation state.\N{\rChinese}学校的目的就是为民族国家服务。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.20,1:05:06.72,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Oh. Right?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？哦。对吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.82,1:05:11.10,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? If you believe in the nation state, if you believe in Mother China, then you must serve her.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？如果你相信民族国家，如果你相信母亲中国，那么你就必须为她服务。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.24,1:05:13.26,English,,0,0,0,,You must obey her. You must fight for her.\N{\rChinese}你必须服从她。你必须为她而战。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.30,1:05:16.40,English,,0,0,0,,You must die for her. Okay? So\N{\rChinese}你必须为她而死。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.40,1:05:18.92,English,,0,0,0,,the idea of the nation state was created\N{\rChinese}民族国家的概念被提出
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.92,1:05:22.68,English,,0,0,0,,in order to make you obedient to authority.\N{\rChinese}以使你服从权威
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.40,1:05:26.56,English,,0,0,0,,And it works very effectively. Yeah?\N{\rChinese}它运作得非常有效。对吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.64,1:05:32.92,English,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering if this only works out in Chinese countries,\N{\rChinese}我只是想知道这是否只在中国等国家有效？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.06,1:05:34.78,English,,0,0,0,,like, all the countries.\N{\rChinese}像，所有国家。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.06,1:05:36.62,English,,0,0,0,,All countries. All countries are nation states.\N{\rChinese}所有国家。所有国家都是民族国家。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.82,1:05:40.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, I mean, like, I'm not saying China is different from other places.\N{\rChinese}好的？我想说的是，我不是说中国和其他地方不一样。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.84,1:05:42.86,English,,0,0,0,,China is exactly the same as other places.\N{\rChinese}中国和其他地方完全一样。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.18,1:05:46.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? What you will learn in this class is how do we get to this place?\N{\rChinese}好的？这门课你将学到的是我们如何到达这个地方？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.98,1:05:49.24,English,,0,0,0,,Because, again, the three things that we learn, okay?\N{\rChinese}因为，刚才说的三件事，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.36,1:05:53.20,English,,0,0,0,,Money. The individual.\N{\rChinese}钱。个人。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.20,1:05:56.92,English,,0,0,0,,The individual. The nation state.\N{\rChinese}个人。民族国家。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.46,1:06:00.98,English,,0,0,0,,These are all ideas and\N{\rChinese}这些都是概念而已
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.98,1:06:04.14,English,,0,0,0,,concepts beyond the human experience.\N{\rChinese}超越人类经验的概念。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.68,1:06:07.96,English,,0,0,0,,If you try to work this out from first principles,\N{\rChinese}如果你从第一原理去推算
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.20,1:06:10.60,English,,0,0,0,,if you try to figure this out by yourself, you couldn't do it.\N{\rChinese}如果你自己想推算出来，做不到的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.64,1:06:14.06,English,,0,0,0,,You have to be brainwashed into believing these three things.\N{\rChinese}你必须被洗脑成相信这三件事。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.30,1:06:17.64,English,,0,0,0,,If someone from the past, maybe a thousand years ago, were to come today,\N{\rChinese}如果过去的某人，或许多年前的某人，今天来到这里，
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.78,1:06:20.72,English,,0,0,0,,and you would explain the concept of money, individual,\N{\rChinese}并且你会解释金钱的概念，个人，
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.98,1:06:24.28,English,,0,0,0,,and nation state, the person would be like, wait a minute here.\N{\rChinese}以及民族国家，那个人会说，等一下。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.04,1:06:29.62,English,,0,0,0,,This means that you're all slaves.\N{\rChinese}这意味着你们全都成了奴隶。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.06,1:06:36.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So, now the question\N{\rChinese}好的？那么，现在的问题是：
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.10,1:06:39.20,English,,0,0,0,,then is, where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}然后是，哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.70,1:06:41.88,English,,0,0,0,,Where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.88,1:06:43.14,English,,0,0,0,,Where do we get these three concepts from? Where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}哪儿得到这三概念？哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.14,1:06:46.56,English,,0,0,0,,Where do we get these three concepts from? Where do we get these three concepts from? Where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}哪儿得到这三概念？哪儿得到这三概念？哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.12,1:06:49.82,English,,0,0,0,,Where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.68,1:06:52.54,English,,0,0,0,,Where do we get these three concepts from?\N{\rChinese}哪儿得到这三概念？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.54,1:06:54.38,English,,0,0,0,,called monotheism.\N{\rChinese}被称为单神论。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.20,1:07:01.56,English,,0,0,0,,The one true God.\N{\rChinese}唯一的真神。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.52,1:07:06.60,English,,0,0,0,,This idea, monotheism,\N{\rChinese}这个概念，单神论。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.74,1:07:10.50,English,,0,0,0,,forever changed the course of human history.\N{\rChinese}永远改变了人类历史的进程。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.68,1:07:13.78,English,,0,0,0,,They gave us these concepts of money, individual,\N{\rChinese}它们给我们带来了钱、个体和民族国家的概念。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.06,1:07:15.76,English,,0,0,0,,and nation -state.\N{\rChinese}and nation -state.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.50,1:07:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,Monotheism is such a powerful idea that\N{\rChinese}单神论是如此强大的概念，
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.96,1:07:26.22,English,,0,0,0,,it turned nothing into everything.\N{\rChinese}它把一无所成为一切。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.92,1:07:29.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's what you will learn in this class.\N{\rChinese}好的，这就是你在这门课里学到的内容。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.08,1:07:33.88,English,,0,0,0,,We will learn about monotheism, we will discover how it created money,\N{\rChinese}我们将学习单神论，探究它如何创造了金钱、个体和民族国家，并且它基本上塑造了我们今天所处的世界。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.04,1:07:38.50,English,,0,0,0,,individual, and the nation -state, and it basically created the world that we live in today.\N{\rChinese}我们将学习单神论，探究它如何创造了金钱、个体和民族国家，并且它基本上塑造了我们今天所处的世界。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.64,1:07:43.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的？好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.22,1:07:45.78,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Any questions?\N{\rChinese}好的。还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.92,1:07:49.00,English,,0,0,0,,Is Christianity monotheistic?\N{\rChinese}基督教是单神论的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.14,1:07:53.12,English,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? Christianity is like monotheistic.\N{\rChinese}请问一下？基督教是单神论的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.14,1:07:55.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah. So there are three great monotheistic religions, right?\N{\rChinese}好的，嗯。 那么有三大单神论宗教，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.94,1:08:00.74,English,,0,0,0,,Judaism, Christianity, and Islam.\N{\rChinese}犹太教、基督教和伊斯兰教。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.88,1:08:07.08,English,,0,0,0,,What I will show you later on is, it's basically the same religion.\N{\rChinese}我稍后要给你展示的，基本上就是同一种宗教。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.16,1:08:10.42,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah. All right.\N{\rChinese}嗯。嗯。好的。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.76,1:08:14.00,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so I don't want to give you too much information, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的，我不想给你太多信息，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.00,1:08:15.96,English,,0,0,0,,Because it's a lot to process.\N{\rChinese}因为这很大
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.28,1:08:17.86,English,,0,0,0,,But I want you guys to remember the concepts.\N{\rChinese}但我想让你们记住这些概念。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.16,1:08:22.14,English,,0,0,0,,Money, individual, and nation -state are all powerful concepts\N{\rChinese}金钱、个人和民族国家都是强大的概念。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.14,1:08:24.60,English,,0,0,0,,that are embedded into everyday life.\N{\rChinese}它们已嵌入日常生活中。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.74,1:08:28.36,English,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape it. Okay, you've been brainwashed into thinking\N{\rChinese}你无法逃脱。好了，你已经被洗脑成这样想。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.36,1:08:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,that they all exist, when in fact, they actually don't exist.\N{\rChinese}它们都存在，实际上却并不存在。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.40,1:08:33.98,English,,0,0,0,,And that's how power works.\N{\rChinese}这就是权力的运作方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.16,1:08:38.66,English,,0,0,0,,What power is, okay, what power truly is,\N{\rChinese}什么是权力，好吗，真正的权力是什么，
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.78,1:08:41.26,English,,0,0,0,,is what we'll call.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们要说的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.26,1:08:44.32,English,,0,0,0,,.. alchemy.\N{\rChinese}炼金术。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.14,1:08:50.84,English,,0,0,0,,Alchemy, throughout human history,\N{\rChinese}炼金术，贯穿人类历史。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.98,1:08:56.70,English,,0,0,0,,was the pursuit of turning lead into gold.\N{\rChinese}铅变成金的追求。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.00,1:08:59.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Lead into gold.\N{\rChinese}铅变成金。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.78,1:09:03.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay?\N{\rChinese}好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.54,1:09:07.18,English,,0,0,0,,Nothing into everything.\N{\rChinese}无到有。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.42,1:09:08.78,English,,0,0,0,,That's what alchemy was.\N{\rChinese}这就是炼金术。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.02,1:09:11.24,English,,0,0,0,,And..\N{\rChinese}和…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.24,1:09:14.26,English,,0,0,0,,. Maybe in science class, you're taught that alchemy is just fake science.\N{\rChinese}也许在科学课上，你们会被教到炼金术只是伪科学。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.42,1:09:16.28,English,,0,0,0,,It's a pseudo -science. And it did not work.\N{\rChinese}它是一门伪科学，且确实没用。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.78,1:09:20.12,English,,0,0,0,,What you will learn in this class is, we achieve alchemy.\N{\rChinese}你将在这门课里学到的，就是我们实现炼金术。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.46,1:09:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? We turn nothing into everything.\N{\rChinese}好吗？我们把无物变成有物。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.46,1:09:25.98,English,,0,0,0,,We turn lead into gold.\N{\rChinese}我们把铅变成金。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.18,1:09:27.68,English,,0,0,0,,Or, that's what power is.\N{\rChinese}或者，这就是力量的本质。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.44,1:09:31.04,English,,0,0,0,,Power is the capacity to turn nothing into everything.\N{\rChinese}力量是把无物变成有物的能力。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.30,1:09:34.50,English,,0,0,0,,Power is the capacity to make you believe that money is valuable.\N{\rChinese}力量是让你相信金钱有价值的能力。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.08,1:09:38.38,English,,0,0,0,,That the individual can lead to happiness.\N{\rChinese}那个人可以走向幸福。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.88,1:09:40.30,English,,0,0,0,,That the nation -state exists.\N{\rChinese}那民族国家存在。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.30,1:09:41.62,English,,0,0,0,,That's what power is.\N{\rChinese}这就是力量的本质。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.82,1:09:45.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And as a result,\N{\rChinese}好的？于是，
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.26,1:09:50.76,English,,0,0,0,,today we live extremely miserable lives.\N{\rChinese}今天我们过着极其悲惨的生活。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.42,1:09:55.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So,\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.04,1:09:59.52,English,,0,0,0,,you've been taught to think that, oh, life just gets better and better.\N{\rChinese}你已经被教会想，哦，生活会越来越好。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.76,1:10:02.68,English,,0,0,0,,What you will learn in this class is, actually,\N{\rChinese}你在这门课里学到的，实际上是，
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.88,1:10:05.48,English,,0,0,0,,nope.\N{\rChinese}不。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.82,1:10:07.98,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And\N{\rChinese}好的吗？而且
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.98,1:10:11.60,English,,0,0,0,,what's really important is, you will also learn in this class\N{\rChinese}真正重要的是，你在这门课里还会学到
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.60,1:10:14.56,English,,0,0,0,,that this was an accident.\N{\rChinese}这是一场意外的事。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.00,1:10:20.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is an accident.\N{\rChinese}好的？这是一场意外的事。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.20,1:10:23.18,English,,0,0,0,,It's an accident of the human imagination.\N{\rChinese}这是一场人类想象的意外。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.78,1:10:28.28,English,,0,0,0,,It's because we didn't know what we were doing that we created this system.\N{\rChinese}因为我们不知道自己在做什么，所以才创造了这个系统。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.14,1:10:32.96,English,,0,0,0,,So, what you will also learn is that, if you're able to control the human imagination,\N{\rChinese}所以，你还会学到的是，如果你能掌控人类想象，
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.96,1:10:37.08,English,,0,0,0,,you can use it to create a new system\N{\rChinese}你可以用它来创造一个新的系统
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.08,1:10:39.98,English,,0,0,0,,that allows for, you know,\N{\rChinese}让它能够实现，你知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.98,1:10:45.40,English,,0,0,0,,eudaimonia, or the flourishing of the human intellect.\N{\rChinese}eudaimonia，即人类智力的繁荣。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.30,1:10:49.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Alright.\N{\rChinese}好吧？好的。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.20,1:10:56.20,English,,0,0,0,,Any questions? Okay.\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？好的。
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.28,1:11:01.80,English,,0,0,0,,So, that's it for today.\N{\rChinese}好了，今天就到此为止。
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.04,1:11:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? I'll see you guys next class. Bye.\N{\rChinese}好的？下节课见。拜拜。
